                    <blockquote cite="https://www.interaction-design.org/literature/topics/usability">
                        Usability is a measure of how well a specific user in a specific context can use a product/design to achieve a defined goal effectively, efficiently and satisfactorily.
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="explanation-card__quote-source">
                        - <a href="https://www.interaction-design.org/literature/topics/usability">Interaction Design Foundation</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="explanation-card d-none d-block d-lg-none" id="what-is-ux">
