                    <blockquote cite="https://www.nngroup.com/articles/definition-user-experience/">
                        &quot;User experience&quot; encompasses all aspects of the end-user's interaction with the company, its services, and its products.
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="explanation-card__quote-source">
                        - <a href="https://www.nngroup.com/articles/definition-user-experience/">Nielsen Norman Group</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="explanation-card d-none d-block d-lg-none" id="why-should-i-care">
